steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/719750/extras/fc7fa1b1e0be3d19e9477726e68788c1.apng?t=1763061946\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/719750/extras/fc7fa1b1e0be3d19e9477726e68788c1.poster.avif?t=1763061946\" class=\"bb_img\" width=22 height=19 /></picture></span>   Free your future partners and they'll help you fight evil!</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/719750/extras/ba9023207cca2dc7f9d4fe0c655f784a.apng?t=1763061946\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/719750/extras/ba9023207cca2dc7f9d4fe0c655f784a.poster.avif?t=1763061946\" class=\"bb_img\" width=22 height=19 /></picture></span>   Compare the results of your run with the results of other players on the leaderboard</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/719750/extras/f464c70f6fd83c0efb6c11604677e365.apng?t=1763061946\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/719750/extras/f464c70f6fd83c0efb6c11604677e365.poster.avif?t=1763061946\" class=\"bb_img\" width=22 height=19 /></picture></span>   The levels are tougher than they look at first sight. They also appear in a random sequence!</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/719750/extras/55c78dbc9b223ba3f5f589fae7d0b0b7.apng?t=1763061946\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/719750/extras/55c78dbc9b223ba3f5f589fae7d0b0b7.poster.avif?t=1763061946\" class=\"bb_img\" width=22 height=19 /></picture></span>   Various skins for your cat :3<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstat